The paper proposes a network for object detection using radar data, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also introduces a cross-modal supervision framework, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and multimodal data processing (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of semantic information, which is a topic related to natural language processing (cs.CL).
